Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.91,0:00:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚少年  鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.35,0:00:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从谜之少女C.C.那里得到了不可思议的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够对任何人下达命令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并让其绝对遵守的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.72,0:00:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了妹妹娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修计划将布里塔尼亚帝国毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的好友枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.97,0:00:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正逐渐在帝国内部确立自己的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.58,0:00:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时至此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后的命运或许已经注定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 8
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.66,0:02:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}黑之骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次走出东京租界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.16,0:02:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修也来就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.73,0:02:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚彻夜长谈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和喜欢的男生互诉衷肠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长你有这样的对象么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.31,0:02:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[河口湖: 位于山梨县东南部的富士五湖之一 观光胜地]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河口湖有很多布里塔尼亚观光客\N治安也很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:02:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会像贫民区那样可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:02:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次不会扔下你不管的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快进来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始 这里就是我们的基地了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个… 可以理解为你愿意和我们合作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我们是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西你是怎么弄到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拜托了一下 他们就送给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向那些只知道吃喝嫖赌的贵族们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么简单就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会留下把柄的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:43.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  还有二楼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这车子会不会太大了点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这样反而可能会成为军队盘查的盲点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连电视都有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现场情况现在怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 这里是河口湖的会议中心酒店(Convention Center Hotel)前方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:03:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劫持酒店的犯人自称是日本解放战线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前他们把以詹姆斯议长为首的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[Sakuradite：产于富士山附近的稀有金属\N确保Sakuradite的供应是布里塔尼亚对日本发动侵略战争的原因之一]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuradite分配会议的与会人员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和正好在场的观光客  以及数名工作人员作为人质
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是犯人送来的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了詹姆斯议长等人以外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能看到学生的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪集团的首领是自称草壁中校的旧日本军人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造高温超导体不可或缺的原料Sakuradite
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是直接影响到世界安全保障的重要战略物资
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AREA-11是世界最大的Sakuradite的产地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占全世界供给量的70%
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年在这里举办的Sakuradite生产国会议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定着Sakuradite的国际分配比率
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说其结果就是我们布里塔尼亚\N和其他诸国的国力之比也不为过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖份子很可能正是看准了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此会议所具有的引发重大国际舆论的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才做出这次挟持酒店的暴行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是日本解放战线的草壁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了日本的独立解放而战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位虽然不是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却是布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妄图支配我们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是乖乖听话就不会伤害你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始行动了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们可是日本最大的反布里塔尼亚势力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然不甘人后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,针对我们吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该高兴还是该悲伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们这样只会和敌方同归于尽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利瓦尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在提示音后留言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种时候他在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接酒店的桥梁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除主桥外 其他全部被切断
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从上空和水下的接近作战全部以失败告终
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下有可能执行人质救出作战的道路只有一条
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:06:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,延伸至会议中心酒店正下方的供给通道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用这条通道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以将地基破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使酒店沉入水中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个通道是为了运送物资而建造
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以即使是Sutherland也可以通过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方肯定对此有所准备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不会有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从以往他们所使用的武器等级来看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全可以回避
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现敌影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和预想一样  从地下通道进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[雷光: 由2台改造过的GLASGOW从2侧支撑起中间的Linear Cannon的特制KnightMare Frame\NLinear Cannon: 通过电磁诱导射出超高速炮弹的炮台]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷光  启动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右四连脚部固定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[超电磁式榴散弹重炮: 装备在雷光中的对KnightMare用大型加农炮\N射出的榴散弹可轻易贯通KnightMare装甲 在限定空间内回避困难]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超电磁式榴散弹重炮  电压确认
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预计会有反KnightMare来福炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散开后突破
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超电磁式榴散弹重炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一击毙命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派上用场了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领教了吧 布里塔尼亚的猪头们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:06:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全灭!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人设置了用Glasgow改造的炮台
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是Linear Cannon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说突破无望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按他们要求 释放政治犯吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能向恐怖份子示弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 尤菲米娅殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这点 应该还未被觉察到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们知道人质中有尤菲米娅殿下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会被用来作为交涉筹码的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为殿下只是作为旁听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以会议名单上没有她的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定会顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我可不是他的监护人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们特派不能参加人质救出作战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然申请是提交了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们是命令系统不同的特殊部门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.37,0:07:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:53.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能把作战交给ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯内莉娅殿下是严格区分布里塔尼亚人和NUMBERS的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:08:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还无法让她认同我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底为了什么才建立名誉布里塔尼亚人制度的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位父亲  你女儿莎莉小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西要放到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里那里 驾驶室那边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 放在这里的箱子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是去观光而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还只是个学生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却被恐怖份子无差别地掳走…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女儿会平安无事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子明明什么坏事都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了与布里塔尼亚作战 组织是必须的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不能就这么袖手旁观
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照柯内莉娅的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会无视人质的存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 为什么到现在她还按兵不动?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人质会怎么样呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没有放过布里塔尼亚人的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是… 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个分给大家可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个… 虽然我是觉得很帅啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们是反抗组织
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不是反抗组织
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传令各特别狙击小队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:13.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持现状
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各小队长进行通报确认…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人质中的学生… 是学生会的同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交涉还在进行 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是组织的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起个人的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.51,0:09:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会以组织的规则优先
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞希尔小姐  那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道  想把人质…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是对我们的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然没有任何回应的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每隔30分钟我们会推一个人质下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了人质 希望你们作出具有诚意的回应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然杀鸡儆猴  那些野蛮人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如我们先暂且同意交涉  至少让他们先放了妇女和孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:09:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦我们进行了交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就代表认同了恐怖份子的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就强攻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个应该是在确保了尤菲米娅殿下的安全之后才可以采取的策略吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.52,0:10:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总督  ZERO…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从ZERO那里传来联络
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三号车被ZERO给偷走了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉姆森在干什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是回过神来车子已经被开走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在那辆三号车呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在军队的正中间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经确认了  是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要实施狙击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持现状 待机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包围完成后 再逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  他所说的正义是什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那之前可能会被杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面的同伴也没有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不用我们自己那辆车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以在众目睽睽之下把自己的基地曝光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以相信他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫ZERO的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我早说了他很可疑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过万一出了什么事 我会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯内莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我很想在这里回报你上次的招待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在利用你还是太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果像预想的一样 就不需要使用Geass了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又见面了呢 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是日本解放战线的成员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说想要协助他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在要以处理我们的事优先
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚弟克洛维斯的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让你在此偿还
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯内莉娅  你选择哪一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已死的克洛维斯 和 活着的尤菲米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好!  果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个条件已经确认了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子没变啊  柯内莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直以来都很溺爱尤菲米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才无法行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情束缚了你的手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来救出尤菲米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:11:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对能救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从布里塔尼亚那里传来的联络
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.38,0:12:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传令全军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让ZERO通过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让ZERO通过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:23.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本解放战线会把我视为同志来欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是当作障碍来清除呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是无法抗拒能与ZERO会面这个诱惑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战的前提条件全部确认
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  总督
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于ZERO的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他们杀死下一个人质的时间应该稍有推迟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这是个好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连同ZERO一网打尽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解 非常感谢您的指名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以出击了 Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是要从正面突破供给通道的Linear Cannon
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是说要把我们当成诱饵来制造破绽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  似乎亲卫队将趁机冲进去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎? 怎么这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞希尔  我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然为了救出大家而需要我和Lancelot的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就应该去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是作为诱饵也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木准尉  现在说明作战概要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据精密探测(Prime Search)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人质都被困在酒店的中间层的食品储藏库里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向导兵器  Z-01  Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用供给通道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移动到酒店地下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达后 破坏酒店的地基
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使酒店沉入水中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人质所在的地方预计可支撑8分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人质的救出及恐怖份子的清除由其他部队负责
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[VARIS: Variable Ammunition Repulsion Impact Spitfire\N手持来福枪,泛用弹药斥力冲击炮,通过Impact Rail的更换可以适应各种战况\NImpact Rail: VARIS的可换装部分 通过该部分可发射各种效果的炮弹\N反物质: 与正物质相对应,正反物质在接触时双方同时湮灭,释放出大量能量]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外为了破坏地基需要使用VARIS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲击能量设定为反物质(Anti-Material)3级
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 剩下的问题就是埋伏于隧道内的Linear Cannon了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于空间受到限制
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以即使是Lancelot  回避率也只有47.8%
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:19.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要在适当的时机回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能把Lancelot弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适当的时机?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个星期天我要和会长还有妮娜去河口湖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 那天我有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 谢谢你邀请我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离作战开始还有12分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.14,0:14:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入倒计时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E… ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道了啦  所以请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快给我纠正
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会纠正的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那算什么口气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来隔壁房间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好教育一下你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我起来  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我和你们的首领见面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  副总督
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是布里塔尼亚第三皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲米娅·Li·布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:38.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想和我联手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就让我们看看你的真面目  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样很无礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在此之前我想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在此次行动的最后  希望得到怎样的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:16:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让国内外都知道日本人还没有死光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真陈腐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们思想真陈腐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无可救药了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什么意思  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[M.V.Booster: 搭载于Lancelot上的超高速移动系统\N发动时Lancelot具有比通常状态更高速的移动性能]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M.V.Booster
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.02,0:16:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lancelot  出发!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应确认
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方KnightMare  一机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移动速度约为普通的两倍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  反正都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超电磁式榴散弹重炮 发射!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:38.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是说了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他本来就不打算作为诱饵  而是准备好好干一场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.86,0:16:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请报告中校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才联络时说的人质带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自称是尤菲米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO  我们已经无话可谈了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校他们已经自行了断了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟到自己此次的行动毫无意义之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了民众挺身而出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  特派的KnightMare
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  照这样下去似乎可以突破
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以期待吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  这程度的破坏力还可以承受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五发也被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要胆怯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[四连腕部自在炮台: 搭载于超电磁式榴散弹重炮的副装备]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四连腕部自在炮台展开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是绝对防卫线 必须死守!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞希尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在这里使用VARIS
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 那太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可滑行领域已经很窄了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已有承受爆炸冲击的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你就任副总督了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲米娅皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并非什么值得高兴的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实  因为克洛维斯死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最后他还在向我乞求饶他一命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:23.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那张下令杀死ELEVEN的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就杀了皇兄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是布里塔尼亚皇帝的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量全开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮身被毁也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要死守到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个ELEVEN…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尔弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的白色机体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:30.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  枢木准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三号摄像机怎么样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是被ZERO拿走了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.81,0:19:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才想要反应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是为此才拿走的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了要利用吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:19:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能拯救成功
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.03,0:20:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被困在酒店里的人质我已全部救出
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就让他们回到你们的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢说如此厚颜无耻的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果对你出手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会反过来利用人质吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬畏我们 追随我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的名字是  黑之骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士团?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讽刺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.49,0:20:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖份子居然自称骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们黑之骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是所有手无寸铁之人的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本解放战线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用卑劣的手段把布里塔尼亚平民当作人质
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨无人道地杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是无意义的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们对此进行了制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.33,0:21:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能停止放映
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,责任?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西由我来承担
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛维斯前总督也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下令虐杀手无寸铁的ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.98,0:21:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法坐视这等残暴的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此也对他进行了制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不否定战争
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,0:21:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强者单方面虐杀弱者这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不允许!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有资格开枪的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那些已有被杀觉悟的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当拥有力量的强者欺凌没有力量的弱者的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将会再次出现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:21:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论那个敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.69,0:22:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有多么强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义的… 使者?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.41,0:22:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有力量的人们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬畏我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.48,0:22:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有力量的人们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.33,0:22:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追随我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.92,0:22:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界 将由我们黑之骑士团来…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲裁!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.73,0:23:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运气来临了 天助我也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.71,0:23:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到能抓住柯内莉娅的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.98,0:23:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲米娅这个弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.07,0:23:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 现在开始就是黑之骑士团的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是我的反击
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.44,0:24:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向禁锢我的 这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.23,0:24:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.19,0:24:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向无法动弹的 我自己的内心
